[h1|Metamagic]Metamagic[/h1]
Metamagic ([section:clr-meta]META[/section]) modifies the next [section:clr-sorc]Sorcery[/section] spell a sorcerer casts in various ways. This results in [url:core#Disadvantage]Disadvantage[/url] (or sometimes [url:core#Advantage]Advantage[/url]) on [url:/generia/rules/magic/chaotic-magic#ChaosCheck]Chaos Checks[/url], indicated by the keyword [section:clr-chaos]CHAOS [X][/section], where [section:clr-value]X[/section] denotes the level of Disadvantage.
[br][i]Negative X implies Advantage.[/i]
